fields.description:
List exhibiting organisations for an event edition.

**Example:**
```
{
  exhibitingOrganisations(eventEditionId: "eve-SOME_GUID", lastModifiedDate:"2019-03-05T14:20:10.8442328Z") {
    companyName, id, organisationId
# Ask for additional fields here, see ExhibitingOrganisation type for full list
    }
}
```

List exhibiting organisations by ids.

**Example:**
```
{
  exhibitingOrganisationsByIds(exhibitingOrganisationsIds: "exh-123,exh-234", locale: "en-GB") {
    companyName, id, organisationId
# Ask for additional fields here, see ExhibitingOrganisationBasicDetailsResponseType type for full list
    }
}
```

xhibiting organisations by id.

**Example:**
```
{
  exhibitingOrganisationBasicDetails(id:"exhibiting-organisation-id",locale:"some-locale"){
    stands{
      name
    }
  }
}
```

List exhibiting organisations (with multilingual fields) for an event edition.

**Example:**
```
{
  exhibitingOrganisationsMultilingual(
    eventEditionId: "eve-660950a9-d15b-4f0b-b26b-171ef48adfcf"
  ) {
    id
    companyName
    companyNameYomigana
    accompanyingWebsiteUrl
    sharerCount
    filterCategories {
      id

      multilingual {
        name
        locale
      }
      responses {
        answerId
        taxonomyId
        parentId
        answerText {
          locale
          name
        }
        multilingual {
          name
          locale
        }
      }
      responseHierarchy {
        text
        multilingual {
          locale
          name
        }
      }
    }
    multilingual {
      coverImageUrl
      addressLine1
      countryCode
      description
    }
    socialMedia {
      url
      name
    }
    stands {
      name
    }
    mboProfileQuestions {
      objectiveId
      responses {
        answerId
        questionId
        taxonomyId
      }
    }
    profileQuestions {
      id
      responses {
        answerId
      }
      responseHierarchy {
        text
        answerId
        answers {
          answerId
          text
          answers {
            answerId
            text
            answers {
              text
              answerId
            }
          }
        }
      }
    }
    products {
      multilingual {
        locale
        title
        description
      }
      id
      lastUpdatedAt
      filterAttributes {
        id
        questionText {
          locale
          name
        }
        responses {
          answerId
          answerText {
            locale
            name
          }
        }
        responseHierarchy {
          answerId
          answerText {
            locale
            name
          }
          answers {
            answerId
            answerText {
              locale
              name
            }
          }
        }
        sortOrder
      }
      attributes {
        id
        questionText {
          locale
          name
        }
        responses {
          answerId
          answerText {
            locale
            name
          }
        }
        textualResponses {
          locale
          textResponse
        }
        sortOrder
      }
      video {
        id
        defaultThumbnailUrl
        customThumbnailUrl
        partnerVideoUuid
      }
    }
    documents {
      id
      exhibitingOrganisationId
      url
      displayName
      size
      documentType
      type
      publishDate
      createdAt
    }
  }
}
```

List of exhibiting organisations modified after the specified date.

**Example:**
```
query{
  exhibitingOrganisationsList(
    lastUpdatedFrom: "2019-03-05T14:20:10.8442328Z"
    first: 10
    offset: 0
    includeNonGbs: true
    eventEditionId: "eve-7754f35c-8c9e-45ef-a1c3-dbd2da9b8014"
  ) {
    exhibitingOrganisations {
      lastUpdatedAt
      companyName
      products {
        documents {
          id
          type
          url
          displayName
          size
        }
        video {
          id
          defaultThumbnailUrl
          customThumbnailUrl
          partnerVideoUuid
        }
      }
      administrators {
        rxContactMasterId
        isPrimaryAdministrator
        jobTitlesMultilingual {
          id
          title {
            locale
            name
          }
        }
      }
      documents {
        id
        exhibitingOrganisationId
        url
        displayName
        size
        documentType
        type
        publishDate
        createdAt
      }
    }
        totalCount
        totalPages
        hasMore
        pageSize
        count
  }
}
```

