List all sponsored categories already
associated to any exhibiting organisation for a given event edition.

**Example:**
```
{
    reservedSponsoredCategories(eventEditionId: "eve-SOME_GUID") {
        id
    }
}
```

Get a list of Job titles.

**Example:**
```
{
        jobTitles(eventEditionId: "eve-7754f35c-8c9e-45ef-a1c3-dbd2da9b8014"){
          id
            eventEditionId
          title{
            name
              locale
          }
        }
      }

```

Get a list of Collected Offer redemption details by the buyer using email

**Example:**
```
query {
                                                          collectedOffers(emailId: "some-email@xyz.com")
                                                          }
                                                          [or]
                                                          query {
                                                          collectedOffers(visitorId: "visitor-id", eventEditionId: "event-edition-id")
                                                          }
```

List all filter groups for an event edition.

Use this query to find out the ids of the filter items if you want to apply them to an exhibitor.

**Example:**
```
{
  filterGroups(eventEditionId: "eve-SOME_GUID") {
    name, id,
    locale,
    items {
      name, id
    }
# Ask for additional fields here, see FilterGroup type for full list
}
}
```

List all products and services for an event edition.

Use this query to find out the ids of the products and services if you want to apply them to an exhibitor.

**Example:**
```
{
  productsAndServicesMultilingual(eventEditionId: "eve-SOME_GUID") {
    id,
    multilingualItems {
      locale, name
    }
  }
}
```

List all extra characteristics for an event edition.

Use this query to find out the ids of the extra characteristics if you want to apply them to an exhibitor.

**Example:**
```
{
  extraCharacteristicsMultilingual(
        eventEditionId: "eve-SOME_GUID",
        type: "extraCharacteristics_type"  # Specific the type - 1/Exhibitor (or) 2/Product, By Default/if not specified it will be for Exhibitor.
    ) {
    id,
    multilingualItems {
      locale, name
    }
  }
}
```

List exhibitor recommendations for a specific visitor for an event edition.

**Example:**
```

        {
          exhibitorRecommendationsMultilingual(
            eventEditionId: "some-eve-id"
            locale: "en-US"
            interfaceLocale: "en-US"
            accessToken: "xxx"
            maxResult: 15
            organisationId: "exh-123"
            source: 2
            registrationId: "reg-123"
            profileResponses: [
              { answerIds: ["12"] }
              { answerIds: ["34"] }
              { answerIds: ["56"] }
              { answerIds: ["78"] }
            ]
          ) {
            categories {
              multilingual {
                locale
                name
              }
              name
              parentName
              source
            }
            description
            id
            isInnovator
            isNewToShow
            link
            logo
            multilingual {
              address {
                city
                country
                countryCode
                state
              }
              description
              locale
              logo
              title
            }
            recommendationType
            stands {
              name
            }
          }
        }
```

Fetch gbs entitlements details

**Example:**
```
 {
                  entitlement(
                    eventEditionCode: "some-ee-code",
                    entitledObjectId: "some-entitlement-id",
                    productType: "some-product-type",
                   ) {
                      entitledObjectId,eventEditionCode,productCode,endDate
                      }
                    }
```

Fetch expiring gbs entitlements details

**Example:**
```
 {
                  expiringEntitlements(
                    endDate: "yyyy-mm-dd",
                    offSet: 0,
                    limit: 10,
                   ) {
                      entitledObjectId,eventEditionCode,productCode,productType,endDate
                      }
                    }
```

Get List of PPS Visitor Profile Questions and Answers

**Example:**
```

        {
          visitorProfileQuestions(eventEditionId: "some-eve-id", locale: "en-GB") {
            answers {
              id
              parentId
              text
              sortOrder
            }
            instructionalText
            maximumResponses
            minimumResponses
            shortDescription
            sortOrder
            text
          }
        }
```

Retrieves the company admin details for the user sending the request

**Example:**
```
{
                loggedInCompanyAdmin(organisationId:"org-e2f12fb6-f4fd-4cb3-b6e2-7106e47a99d5",,
                  eventEditionId:"eve-82c61776-434d-40b3-80a9-beafa091cb73")
                {
	                email
                    rxContactMasterId
                    firstName
                    lastName
                    isPrimaryAdministrator
                    jobTitlesMultilingual {
                      id
                      title {
                        locale
                        name
                      }
                    }
                }
                }
```

List Feature Filter for given EventEditionId

**Example:**
```
{
  featureFilters(eventEditionId: "eve-7754f35c-8c9e-45ef-a1c3-dbd2da9b8014",
            locale: "en-GB") 
 {
  items{
      id,
      multilingualNames{
        name,
        locale
      },
      colourCode
  }
 }
}
```

