Get the exhibitor session

**Example:**
```
{
  exhibitorSessions(exhibitingOrganisationId: "exh-fed9b03e-9c4f-4328-8a63-e8b87b651f78") {
    id
    title
    location
    sessionDate
    startTime
    endTime
    description
    sessionSpeakers {
      name
    }
  }
}
```

List all event editions.

Use this method to find out the id of an event edition.

**Example:**
```
{
    eventEditions(eventEditionGbsCode: "some-eve-gbs-code",isGbsEnabled:false,isGbsSalesEnabled:false) {
        name, id, gbsCode, eventGbsCode, businessUnitGbsCode, businessUnit {id, gbsCode}, defaultCurrencyCode, lastDateEntitlementsCanBeChangedBy, isECommerceEnabled, isAnonymousRegistrationEnabled, isAbnRequired, marketingConsentShortCode, multiEventInfo { primaryEventEditionId, secondaryEventEditionIds }, primaryLocale, supportedLocales, isParticipationEvent, isChatEnabled, isVideoEnabled, registrationMarketingMethod, registrationCharacterSet, openingHours{openingHoursId, localStartTime, localEndTime}, inviteManagerTileEnabled, isConferenceEvent, shopTileEnabled, badgeManagerTileEnabled, isPhotoRequiredForAccess, connectedId, isOnsiteIdCheckEnabled
    }
}
```

List details of an event edition.

**Example:**
```
{
    eventEdition(eventEditionId: "some-eve-id") {
        name, id, gbsCode, eventGbsCode, businessUnitGbsCode, businessUnit {id, gbsCode}, defaultCurrencyCode, lastDateEntitlementsCanBeChangedBy, isECommerceEnabled, isAnonymousRegistrationEnabled, isAbnRequired, marketingConsentShortCode, multiEventInfo { primaryEventEditionId, secondaryEventEditionIds }, primaryLocale, gbsEnabled,supportedLocales, isParticipationEvent, isChatEnabled, isVideoEnabled, registrationMarketingMethod, registrationCharacterSet, openingHours{openingHoursId, localStartTime, localEndTime},webinar(sku:"some-sku"){title,description},webinars{sku,title,description}, shopTileEnabled, isPhotoRequiredForAccess, connectedId, isOnsiteIdCheckEnabled,
         totalExhibitors, lifeCycleStatus, isAtRisk, inviteManagerTileEnabled, isConferenceEvent, badgeManagerTileEnabled, notes, isFinance, exhibitorManualUrl, customerSupportEmail, offerlist{id, eventEditionId, startDate, endDate, isPublished, primaryLocale,sponsor{name, url, logoUrl} offers{offerId title descriptionnWithUrl{value links{text url}} multilingual{locale title description{value links{text url}} exhibitor{id name logoUrl}}}, colocatedShows {eventEditionId}}
    }
}
```

Get the feature toggles

**Example:**
```
query {
  featureToggles{
    offerbox(featureToggle:"SomeFeatureToggleName"){
        isEnabled
          name
    }
}
}

```

Get Event Details

**Example:**
```
{
  event(id: "some-evt-id") {
    id, eventGbsCode, portfolioId, businessUnitId, multilingualDto { locale, name }, eventEditions, supportedInPlatform, gbsEnabled,
    isParticipationEvent, isGbsRegistrationEnabled, isGbsSalesEnabled, isECommerceEnabled, isAnonymousRegistrationEnabled, isAbnRequired, marketingConsentShortCode, isMatchmakingEvent
    company { id, name }, rXEventCode, eventCycle, eventType, top100, businessRelationship, isJointVenture, customerSupportEmail, operatingUnitCode
        }
    }
```

Get Venue Details

**Example:**
```
{
  venue(code: "some-venue-code") {
    code, name, streetAddress1, streetAddress2, streetAddress3, postalCode, city, state, country
  }
}
```

Returns OK for activated event edition and NOT_FOUND for not activated ones.

Use this method to find out if the event edition is activated or not.

**Example:**
```
{
    isEventEditionActivated (
        eventEditionId: "eve-SOME-GUID"
    )
}
```

Retrieve the current users exhibiting organisation ids and coresponding event edition id

**Example:**
```
query{
        exhibitingOrganisationsByUserId(userId: "some-user-id"){
              exhibitingOrganisations{
                id
                eventEditionId
              }
          }
      }
```

Retrieve the current users exhibiting organisation ids and coresponding event edition information

**Example:**
```
{
            userExhibitingOrganisation(
                eventEditionId: "eve-some-guid",
                exhibitingOrganisationId: "exh-some-guid"
                locale: "en-GB")
            {
                exhibitingOrganisationId,
                companyName,
                package,
                eventEditionId,
                eventEditionName,
                isEmperiaEnabled,
                startDate,
                endDate,
                logo {
                    url,
                    height,
                    width
                },
                stands{
                    size,
                    unitOfMeasurement,
                    standType,
                    name
                }
                entitlements{
                    productCode
                    productType
                    consumedValue
                    totalValue
                    productNumber
                }
                badges{
                    id
                    productCode
                    contact{
                        firstName
                        lastName
                        jobTitle
                        email
                    }
                }
            }
        }
```

List stands for an exhibitor and event edition.

**Example:**
```
{
  stands(
    eventEditionId: "eve-56fec72c-4f13-42c1-bd86-dc565aa488ac"
        standIds: ["A0103","B0816"]
        ){
            items{
                id, yLength, xLength, size, sector, pavilion, venueName, exhibitorId
            }
        }
    }
```

Profile Completeness Calculation.

**Example:**
```
query{
  profileCompleteness(exhibitingOrganisationId:"exh-e9b1953d-a611-4a49-9528-051d678e10e2"){
    percentageCompleted
    fields{
      name,
      priority
      isMultilingual
      filled{
        primaryLocale,
        secondaryLocales
      }
    }
  }
}
```

List all features enabled for an event edition.

**Example:**
```
{
    eventEditionFeatureConfigs(eventEditionId: "some-eve-id") {
        exhibitorFeatures
    }
}
```

Get single form definition

**Example:**
```
query {
  formDefinition(eventEditionId: "eve-7754f35c-8c9e-45ef-a1c3-dbd2da9b8014", formCode: "TestForm_1")
        { id, name, type, metadata { confirmationUrl, elements { type, name, label, maxLength, required } } }
    }
```

Get single form response for a form definition

**Example:**
```

            query {
              formResponseSingle(eventEditionId: "eve-a90e31da-d69f-4ee0-964e-1de25ff5a2bf",
              formCode: "66bc96e1-9dd4-4f60-9d41-593be89edc6c",
              responseId: "52b06d81-7fe1-4817-9ba6-5d80a0c01fee"
              ) { responseId, response { key, value } }
            }
```

Get marketing preference privacy models for forms

**Example:**
```
query{ 
    privacyModels 
    {
        id, name, locale, modelType, preferencesConfiguration {defaultMarketingPreference, marketingChannels, includeShowMarketing}
    }
}
```

List participations for an event edition.(First count will default to 200 if no value or higher value is provided)

**Example:**
```
{
  participations(eventEditionId: "eve-SOME_GUID", offset: 0, first: 100, search:"", updatedAfter:"2020/12/03 13:14:05") {
    items{
            firstName,
            lastName,
            multilingual { description, locale },
            exhibitingOrganisation{
              displayName
            }
          }
# Ask for additional fields here, see Participation type for full list
    }
}
```

Participation information for a user in an event edition

**Example:**
```
{
        userParticipation(eventEditionId: "eve-SOME_GUID",userId: "SOME_USER_ID") {
            exhibitingOrganisationId, participationId, registrationId, firstName, lastName
          }
        }
```

Content participations of an user(Network, Blog,Webinar etc)

**Example:**
```
{
          contentParticipation(userId:"some-user-id") {
              blogParticipation(productCode:"some-product-code") {
                blogId
                isActive
              }
              networkParticipation(eventEditionId: "eve-SOME_GUID", portfolioId:"some-portfolio-id") {
                productCode
		            userId
		            isActive
		            registrationId
		            portfolioId
		            eventEditionId
              }
              webinarParticipation(eventEditionId: "eve-SOME_GUID",productCode:"some-product-code") {
                isActive
                joinUrl
              }
            }
        }
```

Participation Feature Filter for a user in an event edition

**Example:**
```
{
  participantFeatureFilters(eventEditionId:"some-event-id", userId:"some-user-id"){
        featureFilterId,
        colourCode,
            multilingualNames{
            name
            locale
        }
    }
}
```

Get all email login redirect uri.

**Example:**
